Package me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.inventory

Enum Class Enchant

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Enchant>
me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.inventory.Enchant
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Enchant>, Constable
public enum Enchant extends Enum<Enchant>
A simple enum that contains all enchantments in Minecraft, with their bukkit enchantment, material, description and max level. Some are renamed to represent their minecraft name.
